		<title>04GOVERNMENT</title>
		<content> The area covered in our grid comes    
 under the control of West Glamorgan   
 County Council. Glyncorrwg is linked  
 with seven other villages to form the 
 Upper Afan Valley Ward and is         
 represented on the county council by  
 two councillors.                      
 The local council is the Borough of   
 Afan the village has one              
 representative on this body.          
 There is also a community council in  
 the area and the village has one      
 representative on this body.          
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
